languages.text: {n}Что-то разглядев в вашем взгляде, Фроше покоренно вздыхает:{/n} "Это так. Никто не способен выдерживать пытки вечно. Он ушел во Врата Септента, в пространственные врата. А я его подвел".
{n}Froscher glimpses something in your eyes and sighs in defeat.{/n} "That's true. No one can endure torture forever. He went into the Porta Septentum, the dimensional gate. And I have failed him."

languages.text: {n}弗罗舍看见了你的眼神，叹了口气，败下阵来。{/n}“您说得没错，没人能永远忍受折磨。他去了塞普坦之港的次元门，而我让他失望了。”
languages.original_text: {n}Froscher glimpses something in your eyes and sighs in defeat.{/n} "That's true. No one can endure torture forever. He went into the Porta Septentum, the dimensional gate. And I have failed him."

languages.text: {n}フロッシャーはあなたの目の中に何かを見つけたかのように負けを認め、ため息をつく。{/n}「あなたの言うとおり、永遠に拷問に耐えられる人などいません。あのお方は、ポルタ・セプテンタム、つまり異次元ゲートに入って行ってしまいました。そして、私はあのお方を失望させてしまった」
languages.original_text: {n}Froscher glimpses something in your eyes and sighs in defeat.{/n} "That's true. No one can endure torture forever. He went into the Porta Septentum, the dimensional gate. And I have failed him."

languages.text: {n}Froscher vislumbra algo en tus ojos y suspira derrotado.{/n} «Es cierto. Nadie puede soportar la tortura eternamente. Entró en Porta Septentum, el portal dimensional. Y yo le he fallado».
languages.original_text: {n}Froscher glimpses something in your eyes and sighs in defeat.{/n} "That's true. No one can endure torture forever. He went into the Porta Septentum, the dimensional gate. And I have failed him."

languages.text: {n}Froscher sieht in deinen Augen etwas und seufzt geschlagen.{/n} "Das stimmt. Niemand kann Folter ewig ertragen. Er ist durch die Porta Septentum gegangen, das Dimensionstor. Und ich habe ihn enttäuscht."
languages.original_text: {n}Froscher glimpses something in your eyes and sighs in defeat.{/n} "That's true. No one can endure torture forever. He went into the Porta Septentum, the dimensional gate. And I have failed him."

languages.text: {n}Froscher semble apercevoir quelque chose dans vos yeux qui lui fait pousser un soupir découragé.{/n} « C'est vrai, nul ne peut supporter la torture éternellement. Il est en route pour le portail dimensionnel de Porta Septentum. Quant à moi, j'ai échoué à ma mission. »
